1
00:00:00,130 --> 00:00:01,840
Um, excuse me.

2
00:00:02,130 --> 00:00:04,250
Are you Kato Natsu-san?

3
00:00:06,090 --> 00:00:08,050
And you are?

4
00:00:08,300 --> 00:00:10,220
Sorry to startle you.

5
00:00:10,220 --> 00:00:14,180
I'm Motomiya Makoto's manager.

6
00:00:14,180 --> 00:00:16,180
My name is Shiono Aoi.

7
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:18,390
Makoto's...

8
00:00:18,390 --> 00:00:22,860
I was just at his place dropping something off,

9
00:00:23,480 --> 00:00:26,030
and I saw the two of you walking together.

10
00:00:26,610 --> 00:00:27,900
Oh...?

11
00:00:28,150 --> 00:00:29,780
I'm sorry to have to ask this,

12
00:00:29,780 --> 00:00:33,160
but could you please
stay away from Motomiya-kun?

13
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:35,330
This is a critical time for him.

14
00:00:35,740 --> 00:00:37,410
I see.

15
00:00:37,950 --> 00:00:40,040
You said this to Yuki too, didn't you?

16
00:00:40,420 --> 00:00:43,420
As his friend, surely you understand.

17
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:46,840
I don't really care about myself,

18
00:00:47,510 --> 00:00:50,760
but Makoto needs Yuki.

19
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:53,050
The only one who can make him shine

20
00:00:53,050 --> 00:00:54,850
is without a doubt, Yuki.

21
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:57,800
As their friend,
I'm warning you.

22
00:00:58,060 --> 00:00:59,520
Now, if you'll excuse me.

23
00:01:08,610 --> 00:01:10,490
Is this really okay?

24
00:01:10,490 --> 00:01:12,780
Meeting up in a place like this?

25
00:01:13,620 --> 00:01:15,120
I don't mind.

26
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:17,120
But it's risky for you, isn't it?

27
00:01:19,540 --> 00:01:20,660
You should go back.

28
00:01:20,660 --> 00:01:21,920
If someone sees us...

29
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,630
Who?

30
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:26,210
You...

31
00:01:26,210 --> 00:01:29,010
You've fallen for someone else, haven't you?
Someone other than me.

32
00:01:31,220 --> 00:01:32,340
What?
